reviewText: Great cast with some action and comedy thrown in.  Script was a little light, but fun to watch.

I was totally surprised when i watched this movie --it is like a small homage to the great films like "Magnificent 7" " " Dirty Dozen " --Robert Davi is Fantastic and wish this had been a big budget film--  it has fun action --some whacky characters -- crisp direction by Brent Huff -- and has heart --- I highly recommend !!!!  and Yes , I am a huge Robert Davi fan --something about him I just love --
